Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.80,0:00:15.80,Main,,0,0,0,,We finally found them!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.89,0:00:17.55,Main,,0,0,0,,This is Star Platinum!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.64,0:00:19.39,Main,,0,0,0,,Kujo Jolyne.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.47,0:00:24.02,Main,,0,0,0,,Did she defeat the guard\Nby herself and take the discs?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.57,0:00:31.99,Main,,0,0,0,,I will return the disc to my father.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.82,0:00:35.28,Main,,0,0,0,,Along with the disc held by Whitesnake…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.86,0:00:36.95,Main,,0,0,0,,No matter what.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.83,0:00:39.91,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Of course.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.99,0:00:45.00,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}All memories relating to myself{\i}\N{\i1}have been deleted from Miraschon's disc.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.67,0:00:48.50,Main,,0,0,0,,Therefore, no one\Nwill be able to track it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.00,0:00:51.50,Main,,0,0,0,,The difference between humans and animals,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.59,0:00:56.05,Main,,0,0,0,,is that humans seek heaven.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.76,0:01:00.47,Main,,0,0,0,,Humans ought to lead a life\Nthat leads them to heaven.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.10,0:01:05.02,Main,,0,0,0,,This is what makes humans beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.28,0:02:39.40,Main,,0,0,0,,{\an8}EPISODE 10: OPERATION SAVAGE GARDEN\N(HEAD TO THE COURTYARD!), PART 1
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.49,0:02:40.95,Main,,0,0,0,,{\an8}-Soap.\N-Here's my rent.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.03,0:02:43.45,Main,,0,0,0,,{\an8}I want the most expensive watch you got.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.33,0:02:45.16,Main,,0,0,0,,Move.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.54,0:02:48.33,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm using the phone next.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.41,0:02:49.71,Main,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.79,0:02:52.63,Main,,0,0,0,,Are you crazy, bitch?\NI'll take real good care of--
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.21,0:03:00.34,Main,,0,0,0,,Take a seat! You won't get tired!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.09,0:03:05.60,Main,,0,0,0,,Here's a complimentary drink.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.18,0:03:08.39,Main,,0,0,0,,Feel free to ask me again.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.24,0:03:24.07,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This is The Speedwagon Foundation HQ{\i}\N{\i1}in Dallas, Texas.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.57,0:03:27.74,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We do not accept{\i}\N{\i1}collect calls on this number.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.83,0:03:31.21,Main,,0,0,0,,I looked up the number in a phonebook.\NI only have this number.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.04,0:03:33.58,Main,,0,0,0,,And I'm an inmate
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.67,0:03:36.71,Main,,0,0,0,,at the Green Dolphin Street\NState Prison in Florida.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.30,0:03:39.09,Main,,0,0,0,,{\an8}My name is Kujo Jolyne.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.67,0:03:41.93,Main,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Please connect me to someone\Nwho knows what this means.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.26,0:03:44.39,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Please hold.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.02,0:03:50.48,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Thank you for waiting.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.31,0:03:54.10,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Are you Professor Kujo Jotaro's daughter?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.19,0:03:55.02,Main,,0,0,0,,And you are?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.61,0:03:57.69,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I am just a foundation representative.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.19,0:04:00.90,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And I am not a Stand User.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.99,0:04:01.90,Main,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.40,0:04:04.66,Main,,0,0,0,,But you seem to know\Nabout Stand abilities.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.74,0:04:07.37,Main,,0,0,0,,Do you know about the discs?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.45,0:04:08.95,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yes, of course.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.58,0:04:13.79,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}After retrieving{\i}\N{\i1}Dr. Kujo Jotaro's body from the UUV,{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.87,0:04:16.83,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}he has been sheltered{\i},{\i1} not here in Dallas,{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.92,0:04:19.50,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}but somewhere safe.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.13,0:04:24.13,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I am so sorry to inform you of this,{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.63,0:04:28.51,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}but your father is medically unresponsive.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.60,0:04:33.35,Main,,0,0,0,,If I say that we can bring him\Nback to life, will you believe me?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.94,0:04:36.81,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I am merely a scientist. I cannot comment.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.31,0:04:38.86,Main,,0,0,0,,I have obtained a disc.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.94,0:04:40.11,Main,,0,0,0,,Just one of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.19,0:04:41.73,Main,,0,0,0,,We can bring him back.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.82,0:04:44.74,Main,,0,0,0,,I just know that\Nthe discs will bring him back.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.91,0:04:48.87,Main,,0,0,0,,I'll do whatever it takes\Nto deliver them to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.95,0:04:50.91,Main,,0,0,0,,I just don't know how to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.49,0:04:55.71,Main,,0,0,0,,I want you to come up\Nwith a plan to deliver the discs there.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.79,0:04:56.83,Main,,0,0,0,,Immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.54,0:05:00.67,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Isn't this conversation{\i}\N{\i1}being recorded by the prison?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.84,0:05:03.80,Main,,0,0,0,,Yes, probably.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.88,0:05:06.34,Main,,0,0,0,,But that's a risk I'm willing to take.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.43,0:05:07.80,Main,,0,0,0,,I have no time.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.89,0:05:09.76,Main,,0,0,0,,This is urgent.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.56,0:05:14.35,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm in a dangerous situation\Nwhere I cannot hide the disc anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.89,0:05:17.90,Main,,0,0,0,,There must be a way.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.98,0:05:21.52,Main,,0,0,0,,And just so you know,\NI am not allowed visitors.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.61,0:05:22.53,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I understand.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.61,0:05:24.57,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Since you insist…{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.03,0:05:27.45,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What about the courtyard?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.53,0:05:28.66,Main,,0,0,0,,The courtyard?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.45,0:05:32.83,Main,,0,0,0,,Do you mean the courtyard\Nbetween the men's and women's prisons?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.91,0:05:33.95,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yes.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.04,0:05:36.04,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Please be there in 20 minutes.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.62,0:05:38.25,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I can manage something.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.33,0:05:40.75,Main,,0,0,0,,In 20 minutes?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.84,0:05:41.79,Main,,0,0,0,,From now?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.50,0:05:44.26,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yes. You said this is urgent.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.13,0:05:49.22,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If you instruct us to retrieve the discs,{\i}\N{\i1}we will do everything we can to do so.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.30,0:05:52.14,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If you say he will be revived,{\i}\N{\i1}we believe you.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.72,0:05:53.56,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}However,{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.14,0:05:57.73,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}we are a non-militaristic{\i}\N{\i1}medical research foundation.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.81,0:05:59.48,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We neither have the resources{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.56,0:06:03.48,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}nor the ability to help you escape{\i}\N{\i1}or save your life.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.23,0:06:06.78,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Is that risk acceptable to you?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.36,0:06:09.28,Main,,0,0,0,,Okay. I'll be there.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.86,0:06:12.58,Main,,0,0,0,,And how will you retrieve the disc?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.66,0:06:15.24,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We shouldn't speak of that over the phone.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.83,0:06:19.21,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But please look for Savage Garden.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.29,0:06:20.96,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You will understand then.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.79,0:06:25.51,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Let's call it{\i}\N{\i1}Operation Savage Garden for now.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.76,0:06:31.39,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Savage Garden…{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.47,0:06:33.10,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Is that an object?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.18,0:06:34.64,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Or is it a person?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.22,0:06:36.52,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Fine.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.60,0:06:38.35,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I need to head to the courtyard.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.10,0:06:41.23,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm at the cafeteria{\i}\N{\i1}of the women's prison.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.31,0:06:45.19,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}To get to the courtyard,{\i}\N{\i1}first, I must pass through the gate,{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.27,0:06:47.03,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}go up the stairs in the back,{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.61,0:06:49.24,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}cross the second floor corridor{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.32,0:06:52.24,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}to get to the medical wing{\i}\N{\i1}from the women's prison.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.32,0:06:53.70,Main,,0,0,0,,You may pass.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.87,0:06:59.79,Main,,0,0,0,,FE40536, you're the nuisance\Nwho got sent to the Punishment Ward.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.87,0:07:03.46,Main,,0,0,0,,Your access to different parts\Nof the facility is restricted.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.39,0:07:15.22,Main,,0,0,0,,Jolyne.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.72,0:07:16.60,Main,,0,0,0,,Emporio!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.68,0:07:19.18,Main,,0,0,0,,Here! Do not touch the ball.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.61,0:07:27.48,Main,,0,0,0,,We can't let others see us.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.07,0:07:28.90,Main,,0,0,0,,Come with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.41,0:07:38.29,Main,,0,0,0,,Wha…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.75,0:07:48.00,Main,,0,0,0,,Emporio, those two…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.63,0:07:50.67,Main,,0,0,0,,It's fine, they can be trusted.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.26,0:07:53.63,Main,,0,0,0,,He prefers to sleep on a bed,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.72,0:07:55.97,Main,,0,0,0,,but this room doesn't have one.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.05,0:07:59.02,Main,,0,0,0,,So he ends up sleeping in the piano.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.65,0:08:11.78,Main,,0,0,0,,Jolyne, I live in secret\Nin this ghost of a room.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.86,0:08:13.32,Main,,0,0,0,,Ghost of a room?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.40,0:08:15.87,Main,,0,0,0,,Does that mean you're…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.95,0:08:17.16,Main,,0,0,0,,No, Jolyne.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.74,0:08:19.62,Main,,0,0,0,,He and I are alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.70,0:08:21.20,Main,,0,0,0,,We aren't ghosts.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.29,0:08:23.87,Main,,0,0,0,,You can touch us.\NWe're warm and have pulses.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.50,0:08:25.54,Main,,0,0,0,,Listen closely.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.17,0:08:30.51,Main,,0,0,0,,Ghosts do not live here,\Nbut the building itself is a ghost.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.42,0:08:33.55,Main,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.63,0:08:35.64,Main,,0,0,0,,Does "the ghost of objects" make sense?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.22,0:08:41.14,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This prison caught fire in 1984{\i}\N{\i1}and went through a huge renovation.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.22,0:08:43.98,Main,,0,0,0,,This room burned down in that fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.19,0:08:47.48,Main,,0,0,0,,This room belongs in the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.56,0:08:49.27,Main,,0,0,0,,It's a ghost of the music room.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.57,0:08:54.11,Main,,0,0,0,,So… this means… Emporio,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.61,0:08:55.45,Main,,0,0,0,,are you…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.16,0:08:57.49,Main,,0,0,0,,Ever since I was born,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.57,0:09:00.33,Main,,0,0,0,,I've been able to materialize\Nthe ghosts of objects.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.04,0:09:03.04,Main,,0,0,0,,That's my Stand ability.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.87,0:09:06.25,Main,,0,0,0,,But I can only use them.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.04,0:09:10.21,Main,,0,0,0,,So even this chocolate bar\Nand this orange juice…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.67,0:09:15.72,Main,,0,0,0,,I can't consume them.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.80,0:09:18.47,Main,,0,0,0,,But they still have a taste.\NThey're quite good.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.68,0:09:24.52,Main,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.06,0:09:26.06,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Don't worry.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.14,0:09:29.65,Main,,0,0,0,,This clock stopped\Nwhen it burned along with the room.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.40,0:09:33.28,Main,,0,0,0,,You still have time\Nbefore your 20 minutes are up.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.36,0:09:34.44,Main,,0,0,0,,But…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.82,0:09:38.82,Main,,0,0,0,,you made a plan to deliver the disc\Nover the phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.91,0:09:40.12,Main,,0,0,0,,How reckless!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.78,0:09:43.37,Main,,0,0,0,,I understand your situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.45,0:09:46.16,Main,,0,0,0,,Whitesnake will learn about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.29,0:09:48.62,Main,,0,0,0,,Please, Emporio.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.71,0:09:51.17,Main,,0,0,0,,Tell me how I can reach the courtyard.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.25,0:09:52.84,Main,,0,0,0,,Don't misunderstand me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.92,0:09:56.84,Main,,0,0,0,,I can't access just any place\Nfrom this ghost room.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.92,0:10:00.64,Main,,0,0,0,,I use the ghost items like this
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.72,0:10:03.56,Main,,0,0,0,,to get around without getting caught.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.43,0:10:06.56,Main,,0,0,0,,I know you have no choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.14,0:10:08.81,Main,,0,0,0,,He says he wants to tag along.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.90,0:10:12.48,Main,,0,0,0,,You should take him.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.57,0:10:13.77,Main,,0,0,0,,He can aid your cause.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.32,0:10:17.95,Main,,0,0,0,,His name is Weather Report.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.62,0:10:26.12,Main,,0,0,0,,This is a music room.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.12,0:10:30.58,Main,,0,0,0,,Don't be so alarmed.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.08,0:10:34.71,Main,,0,0,0,,Weather doesn't talk much\Nbecause he has no memory.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.80,0:10:36.26,Main,,0,0,0,,-Memory?\N-Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.88,0:10:40.89,Main,,0,0,0,,He has no memory of his childhood\Nor when he arrived here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.01,0:10:44.01,Main,,0,0,0,,He's serving a six-year sentence.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.60,0:10:47.35,Main,,0,0,0,,He has a habit of walking on tip-toes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.43,0:10:49.73,Main,,0,0,0,,He's a TV guide fanatic,\Nbut he doesn't watch TV.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.31,0:10:52.77,Main,,0,0,0,,When he talks, he barely opens his mouth.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.86,0:10:55.19,Main,,0,0,0,,And he talks right up to your face,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.27,0:10:57.49,Main,,0,0,0,,so you may feel his lukewarm breath.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.07,0:10:59.53,Main,,0,0,0,,He has no memory?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.61,0:11:02.57,Main,,0,0,0,,Is that because\NWhitesnake stole them from him?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.66,0:11:03.57,Main,,0,0,0,,Probably.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.08,0:11:06.87,Main,,0,0,0,,He wants to learn about himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.95,0:11:12.17,Main,,0,0,0,,He also wants to know\Nwhy Whitesnake wants your father's discs.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.75,0:11:21.72,Main,,0,0,0,,He says his Stand ability\Nis not tied to the discs.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.59,0:11:24.72,Main,,0,0,0,,He was born a Stand User.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.39,0:11:26.47,Main,,0,0,0,,As for his ability…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.35,0:11:33.02,Main,,0,0,0,,he can manipulate the weather to his will.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.56,0:11:35.82,Main,,0,0,0,,His Stand name is…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.98,0:11:40.28,Main,,0,0,0,,Weather Report.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.38,0:12:03.47,Main,,0,0,0,,Pretend you didn't notice him.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.05,0:12:10.93,Main,,0,0,0,,Someone was peeking to see\Nwhere the music was coming from.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.52,0:12:14.44,Main,,0,0,0,,Now it's confirmed.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.02,0:12:17.27,Main,,0,0,0,,Someone knows you made a move
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.94,0:12:20.19,Main,,0,0,0,,and came to check on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.07,0:12:23.49,Main,,0,0,0,,And we now know his face.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.08,0:12:31.95,Main,,0,0,0,,{\an8}STAND NAME: JUMPIN' JACK FLASH\NSTAND MASTER: LANG RANGLER
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.72,0:12:48.01,Main,,0,0,0,,Dammit. He's already close.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.10,0:12:52.31,Main,,0,0,0,,But if he's a Stand User,\Nwe need to take care of him now!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.39,0:12:53.60,Main,,0,0,0,,No, Jolyne.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.68,0:12:55.23,Main,,0,0,0,,We should hide for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.81,0:12:59.36,Main,,0,0,0,,He doesn't know that\Nyou're headed for the courtyard.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.94,0:13:01.73,Main,,0,0,0,,He didn't hear your phone call
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.82,0:13:04.11,Main,,0,0,0,,and that's why came to eavesdrop!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.70,0:13:08.24,Main,,0,0,0,,If he knew, he would have\Nwaited at the courtyard.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.32,0:13:10.83,Main,,0,0,0,,That's why, right now,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.91,0:13:12.37,Main,,0,0,0,,he's chasing us!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.46,0:13:18.46,Main,,0,0,0,,What's up with him?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.04,0:13:22.38,Main,,0,0,0,,Turn into that corner\Nbefore he gets any closer. Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.23,0:13:42.32,Main,,0,0,0,,Just as I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.90,0:13:45.69,Main,,0,0,0,,He doesn't know
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.45,0:13:49.74,Main,,0,0,0,,where you're going yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.82,0:13:52.41,Main,,0,0,0,,But what's with him?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.49,0:13:54.50,Main,,0,0,0,,He had a weird way of running.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.16,0:13:58.58,Main,,0,0,0,,We were able to hide because he's slow.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.67,0:14:02.34,Main,,0,0,0,,Anyway, you need to head to the courtyard.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.92,0:14:05.97,Main,,0,0,0,,Your phone call earlier\Nwas definitely recorded,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.05,0:14:09.39,Main,,0,0,0,,but I don't think Whitesnake heard it yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.47,0:14:12.10,Main,,0,0,0,,The sooner you go,\Nthe less dangerous it'll be.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.60,0:14:14.35,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The medical wing is up ahead.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.97,0:14:17.39,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Once you go downstairs{\i}\N{\i1}and pass the medical wing,{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.48,0:14:19.27,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}there's a gate for the corridor.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.77,0:14:21.36,Main,,0,0,0,,{\an8\i1}It leads to the factory.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.44,0:14:24.28,Main,,0,0,0,,{\an8\i1}It also leads to the men's prison{\i}\N{\i1}across the courtyard.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.36,0:14:27.40,Main,,0,0,0,,The medical wing is accessed\Nby both men and women.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.49,0:14:29.74,Main,,0,0,0,,Weather Report is a man,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.82,0:14:32.03,Main,,0,0,0,,so if tells a guard\Nhe's going back to the men's prison,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.12,0:14:34.95,Main,,0,0,0,,he'll have no problem\Ngetting to the connecting corridor
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.04,0:14:37.29,Main,,0,0,0,,and getting to the factory entrance.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.37,0:14:38.21,Main,,0,0,0,,Go on ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.33,0:14:42.00,Main,,0,0,0,,I need to bribe the guards, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.67,0:14:43.92,Main,,0,0,0,,Is 50 dollars enough?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.00,0:14:47.21,Main,,0,0,0,,Tell them you want your boots repaired\Nat the factory.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.30,0:14:49.76,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But even if you manage{\i}\N{\i1}to pass the medical wing,{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.30,0:14:54.18,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}you'll have to get to{\i}\N{\i1}the courtyard by force.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.10,0:14:58.06,Main,,0,0,0,,The security is light,\Nbut if you get caught, they'll shoot.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.14,0:15:01.06,Main,,0,0,0,,and you'll get five more years\Nfor trying to escape.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.15,0:15:03.11,Main,,0,0,0,,By force, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.61,0:15:05.52,Main,,0,0,0,,Guess I have to get used to using it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.65,0:15:07.94,Main,,0,0,0,,I just have to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.03,0:15:12.45,Main,,0,0,0,,Another five years\Nis nothing at this point.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.53,0:15:14.07,Main,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Emporio.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.16,0:15:15.08,Main,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.78,0:15:17.20,Main,,0,0,0,,This is the most I can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.79,0:15:19.16,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Please revive him.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.00,0:15:23.04,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If your father comes back to life,{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.13,0:15:24.13,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}then I think{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.63,0:15:28.67,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I might be able see some hope.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.60,0:15:36.72,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, dammit.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.81,0:15:38.77,Main,,0,0,0,,What's wrong with this cola?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.85,0:15:41.44,Main,,0,0,0,,You touched the can, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.10,0:15:45.52,Main,,0,0,0,,Did you shake the can?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.61,0:15:47.65,Main,,0,0,0,,Get me another one, will you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.73,0:15:49.99,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, I didn't touch it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.07,0:15:53.49,Main,,0,0,0,,I only touched the plate.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.24,0:15:57.28,Main,,0,0,0,,My shoe's got a hole on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.37,0:15:59.83,Main,,0,0,0,,Over in the back. Can you see it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.91,0:16:02.33,Main,,0,0,0,,I wanted to get it repaired\Nat the factory.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.17,0:16:07.54,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, man, my cola spilled.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.63,0:16:09.88,Main,,0,0,0,,Where did I put that washrag?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.27,0:16:22.77,Main,,0,0,0,,"Go get a cola"?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.85,0:16:24.94,Main,,0,0,0,,You really want me to get one?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.81,0:16:29.19,Main,,0,0,0,,And you want me to pour it into this cup?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.27,0:16:32.03,Main,,0,0,0,,Do that yourself why don't you…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.38,0:16:50.46,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What's going on?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.96,0:16:53.01,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, here's the washrag.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.51,0:16:57.43,Main,,0,0,0,,You can go. But make sure\Nto be back here in 20 minutes…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.05,0:17:00.06,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, she already left.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.97,0:17:02.81,Main,,0,0,0,,What? Where's my cup and the plate?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.98,0:17:05.98,Main,,0,0,0,,What's happening?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.65,0:17:07.52,Main,,0,0,0,,Could it be…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.53,0:17:13.03,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This is…{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.11,0:17:15.70,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The plate is floating!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.78,0:17:17.24,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The cup and the boot as well.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.32,0:17:20.91,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But, the contents of the cup{\i}\N{\i1}aren't spilling out.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.99,0:17:23.12,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It turns into balls of liquid and floats!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.20,0:17:27.75,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Everything I touch is floating upwards!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.83,0:17:31.71,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That money must have floated out{\i}\N{\i1}of that guard's pocket!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.80,0:17:34.51,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm in the air too.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.59,0:17:38.18,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Since when that strange guy{\i}\N{\i1}started chasing me...?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.76,0:17:41.35,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He spit at me then.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.43,0:17:42.56,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Did that cause this?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.35,0:17:45.18,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The disc!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.02,0:17:48.65,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Dammit. It slipped out when I rotated!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.73,0:17:50.61,Main,,0,0,0,,Stone Free!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.61,0:17:54.23,Main,,0,0,0,,My thread! I can't control it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.32,0:17:56.24,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}There is no up and down.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.74,0:17:58.74,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}There's no gravity!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.82,0:18:00.99,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm in zero gravity!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.08,0:18:02.99,Main,,0,0,0,,You're going back to the men's prison?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.95,0:18:06.25,Main,,0,0,0,,Okay. Go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.34,0:18:14.46,Main,,0,0,0,,This is bad! He'll take my disc!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.55,0:18:18.43,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If I try to punch, I'll lose my balance.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.51,0:18:20.30,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I need to focus.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.39,0:18:22.60,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Aim in a single direction like a rocket!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.52,0:18:34.27,Main,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.49,0:18:43.95,Main,,0,0,0,,Dammit. I can't destroy this disc.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.45,0:18:47.70,Main,,0,0,0,,It just comes back like rubber.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.29,0:18:52.96,Main,,0,0,0,,That's why Whitesnake\Ntold me to just collect it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.46,0:18:57.46,Main,,0,0,0,,Hold on!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.14,0:19:02.51,Main,,0,0,0,,Weather Report,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.59,0:19:03.85,Main,,0,0,0,,don't go any further!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.93,0:19:06.35,Main,,0,0,0,,Can you hear me? I'm being attacked!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.43,0:19:08.18,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He took my disc.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.27,0:19:10.85,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If we lose him now, everything is over.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.94,0:19:12.81,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Everything will end!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.44,0:19:14.73,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Don't let him go!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.65,0:19:16.57,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}No…{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.11,0:19:19.11,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}My voice can't reach him.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.79,0:19:29.12,Main,,0,0,0,,What a nuisance.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.08,0:19:34.29,Main,,0,0,0,,Kujo Jolyne,\NI thought I only needed to kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.46,0:19:40.34,Main,,0,0,0,,Jumpin' Jack Flash!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.72,0:19:45.47,Main,,0,0,0,,Weather Report,\Nhis ability takes away gravity.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.55,0:19:48.43,Main,,0,0,0,,Do not touch whatever it is he projects.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.52,0:19:50.18,Main,,0,0,0,,You'll become weightless!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.02,0:19:52.85,Main,,0,0,0,,Zero gravity.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.94,0:19:55.23,Main,,0,0,0,,So you are a Stand User yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.31,0:19:57.73,Main,,0,0,0,,Surely, you understand
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.32,0:19:59.94,Main,,0,0,0,,the implications of my ability.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.62,0:20:08.12,Main,,0,0,0,,He projected
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.29,0:20:10.83,Main,,0,0,0,,pieces of junk.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.79,0:20:14.21,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Weather Report.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.29,0:20:18.13,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This man, who is said to{\i}\N{\i1}control the weather,{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.21,0:20:19.84,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}is a mystery to me.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.92,0:20:24.18,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But that cloud-like thing{\i}\N{\i1}must be a layer of air.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.26,0:20:27.72,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He used its resistance{\i}\N{\i1}to deflect the enemy's attack.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.80,0:20:31.31,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And he's using{\i}\N{\i1}centrifugal force to spin his arm.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.39,0:20:32.73,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's weightless,{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.81,0:20:35.44,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}it can accelerate forever{\i}\N{\i1}with that spinning force.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.02,0:20:38.19,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}His body's center of gravity won't change,{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.27,0:20:40.90,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}so he can accurately project{\i}\N{\i1}a powerful attack.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.11,0:20:46.62,Main,,0,0,0,,Jumpin' Jack Flash!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.70,0:20:48.20,Main,,0,0,0,,Weather Report!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.29,0:20:53.46,Main,,0,0,0,,This flame!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.96,0:20:55.25,Main,,0,0,0,,Aerodynamic friction?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.33,0:20:58.71,Main,,0,0,0,,Dammit, it's spreading!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.79,0:21:00.59,Main,,0,0,0,,Zero gravity, deactivate!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.38,0:21:04.72,Main,,0,0,0,,Meet your end!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.80,0:21:06.43,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Corridor 7B.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.51,0:21:09.39,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Emergency alarm activated.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.89,0:21:13.56,Main,,0,0,0,,Dammit. That impact…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.64,0:21:15.85,Main,,0,0,0,,And I have the disc, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.94,0:21:18.52,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The gate is closing.{\i}\N{\i1}What do I do?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.61,0:21:21.07,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's even harder{\i}\N{\i1}to get to the courtyard now.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.57,0:21:23.44,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But I have no choice.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.53,0:21:25.03,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The enemy will be trapped too!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.11,0:21:27.07,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This is my chance to get back the disc!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.71,0:21:37.17,Main,,0,0,0,,What the hell?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.08,0:21:41.09,Main,,0,0,0,,Everything you touch…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.05,0:21:46.59,Main,,0,0,0,,becomes weightless… Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.88,0:21:49.14,Main,,0,0,0,,Kujo Jolyne?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.82,0:22:10.20,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The courtyard is just ahead.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.28,0:22:13.12,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But where did he go?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.62,0:22:15.33,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I need to get the disc back!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.16,0:23:46.17,Main,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Subtitle translation by: Megumi Hunter
